---
title: Lighter Fish and Chips with Broccoli and DIY Tarter Sauce
description: Forget the excessively fried, more-batter-than-fillet version of fish and chips. We’ve come up with a riff that features a lighter panko breadcrumb crust that’s just as crisp and crunchy. The DIY tartar sauce might just steal the spotlight away from the fish, though. Featuring a breath of fresh dill and crunchy cucumber bits, it totally trumps the kind from a jar.
